This plugin uses javascript to supply extened information about the settings on the options page.
When on the options page mousing over an option label will trigger extended help information about
that setting in the upper right of the page. To enable this plugin add or uncomment the following
in your hastymail2.conf file:

plugin = js_help

Don't forget to rebuild your hastymail2.rc file after changing the hastymail2.conf file. If you
are logged in logout and back in to activate the plugin.
